)@@G@@CL ^[DD0)E-CDDN^[NC(LE( D1#C*,@B@@@@^@)^@)^@)^@)^@) S$CTJCK$^@)^@) 0)CTJOS
)@@G@@CLJD))@C@@@@^@)^@)^@)^@)^@) S$C1JEK$^@)^@) 0)C1J*[@@@@*SDFF*@G@@@@      OT
)@@G@@    . THIS ROUTINE HANDLES ALL FORMS OF LOCATE, FIND AND CHANGE   @^@@@@OU
)@@G@@          . COMMANDS.   @^@@@@          AXR$      .   @^@@@@          EDOV
)@@G@@PC      .   @^@@@@$(1)      . I BANK CODE.@^@@@@          LIT     .     OW
)@@G@@@ @@@@          ASCII   . SET ASCII.@G@@@@.         THIS SECTION OF CODEOX
)@@G@@ HANDLES VARIOUS FORMS OF 'FIND' COMMANDS.@[@@@@.     @E@@@@SNOOP     EQOY
)@@G@@U       0                 . SET SNOOPY FLAG.    @D@@@@OLDC      EQU     OZ
)@@G@@  1                 . TURN ON OLD.  @G@@@@          . THE ENTRIES BELOW PA
)@@G@@ARE OLD COMMANDS WHICH WILL BE DROPPED    @^@@@@          . SOMEDAY..   PB
)@@G@@@E@@@@          ON        OLDC              . ASM IF OLD REQUIRED.@#@@@@PC
)@@G@@FP1*      . FP    @B@@@@          LMJ       X9,LFMOD          .   @C@@@@PD
)@@G@@          S         X9,PTFLG          . SET.    @E@@@@          J       PE
)@@G@@  FIND11            . ENTER BELOW MOD GET.@#@@@@FCD1*     . FCD.  @B@@@@PF
)@@G@@          LMJ       X9,LFMOD          .   @B@@@@          S         X9,FPG
)@@G@@LDFLG         .   @D@@@@          J         FC11              . SET FC TPH
)@@G@@OO.   @#@@@@FD1*      . FD.   @B@@@@          LMJ       X9,LFMOD        PI
)@@G@@  .   @B@@@@          S         X9,FLDFLG         .   @B@@@@          J PJ
)@@G@@        FIND11            .   @#@@@@FC1*      . FC    @B@@@@          LMPK
)@@G@@J       X9,LFMOD          .   @]@@@@FC11      . @B@@@@          S       PL
)@@G@@  X9,LCFLG          .   @B@@@@          S         X9,NLMOD          .   PM
)@@G@@@B@@@@          J         FIND11            .   @C@@@@          . INSERTPN
)@@G@@  LOCATE OLD FORMS HERE, TOO. @#@@@@LP1*      . LP    @B@@@@          LMPO
)@@G@@J       X9,LFMOD          .   @B@@@@          S         X9,PTFLG        PP
)@@G@@  .   @B@@@@          J         LOC1A             .   @]@@@@LCD1*     . PQ
)@@G@@@B@@@@          LMJ       X9,LFMOD          .   @B@@@@          S       PR
)@@G@@  X9,FLDFLG         .   @B@@@@          J         LC11              .   PS
)@@G@@@]@@@@LD1*      . @B@@@@          LMJ       X9,LFMOD          .   @B@@@@PT
)@@G@@          S         X9,FLDFLG         .   @B@@@@          J         LOC1PU
)@@G@@A             .   @]@@@@LC1*      . @B@@@@          LMJ       X9,LFMOD  PV
)@@G@@        .   @]@@@@LC11      . @B@@@@          S         X9,LCFLG        PW
)@@G@@  .   @B@@@@          S         X9,NLMOD          .   @B@@@@          J PX
)@@G@@        LOC1A             .   @B@@@@          OFF       . END OLD COMMANPY
)@@G@@DS.   @ @@@@FIND1*    . ENTRY FOR 'F'.    @E@@@@          SZ        FFAIPZ
)@@G@@L             . CLEAR FAIL FLAG.    @F@@@@          LMJ       X9,LFMOD  QA
)@@G@@        . SET UP ANY SUBFIELDS.     @F@@@@          LMJ       X9,LFCHK  QB
)@@G@@        . CHECK ON TEXT OR DUP.     @F@@@@          LMJ       X9,LFCOP  QC
)@@G@@        . IF TEXT PRESENT, SAVE IT. @D@@@@          TZ        LSFLG     QD
)@@G@@        . WAS 'LS' SET. @E@@@@          J         FIND3             . YEQE
)@@G@@S, BYPASS EXIT.   @^@@@@FIND11    . **TEMP**.   @E@@@@          L       QF
)@@G@@  X7,RPTK           . SET REPEAT IN CASE. @E@@@@          L         X8,NQG
)@@G@@LIMT          . SET SCAN LIMIT.     @]@@@@FIND2     . @G@@@@          TZQH
)@@G@@        LSFLG             . IF WITHIN CURRENT, EXIT HERE.   @C@@@@      QI
)@@G@@    J         NXRQ              . DO IT.  @B@@@@FIND3     . BY PASS FOR QJ
)@@G@@'S' SET ENTRY.    @G@@@@          LMJ       X9,NEXTIM         . GET, DELQK
)@@G@@, PRINT NEXT IMAGE.     @D@@@@          J         FIND9             . ENQL
)@@G@@D OF SCAN.  @D@@@@          L         A2,(1,2)          . SET UP TO     QM
)@@G@@@H@@@@          A         A2,EDCT           . POINT TO START OF STRING OQN
)@@G@@N CMND.     @H@@@@          L         A3,(1,0)          . SET TO POINT TQO
)@@G@@O RIGHT COL IN IMAGE.   @E@@@@          TNZ       ACVAR             . TEQP
)@@G@@ST IF 'LCOL' USED.@C@@@@          J         FIND31            . NO.     QQ
)@@G@@@E@@@@          L         A10,LCOLC         . YES, GET CURRENT.   @B@@@@QR
)@@G@@          TZ        A10               .   @C@@@@          AN,U      A10,QS
)@@G@@1             . LESS 1. @]@@@@FIND31    . @E@@@@          A         A3,AQT
)@@G@@10            . ADD COL PTR IF ANY. @D@@@@          L         A7,(1,0)  QU
)@@G@@        . SET UP FOR    @E@@@@          A,H2      A7,LENGTH         . LIQV
)@@G@@NE LENGTH TEST.   @F@@@@          TG        A3,A7             . TEST IF QW
)@@G@@ALREADY OFF END.  @C@@@@          J         FIND8             . YES.    QX
)@@G@@@A@@@@FIND4     . RENTRY FOR NEXT CHAR.   @D@@@@          L         A4,EQY
)@@G@@DIT81,A2      . GET EDIT CHAR.@E@@@@          L         A5,IMAG80,*A3   QZ
)@@G@@  . GET IMAGE CHAR.     @G@@@@          TNE       A4,TRCHF          . CHRA
)@@G@@ECK IF EDIT CHAR IS TRANSP.   @C@@@@          J         FIND5           RB
)@@G@@  . IT IS.  @E@@@@          TLE       A7,A3             . TEST IF OFF ENRC
)@@G@@D.    @F@@@@          J         FIND8             . YES. NOTE THAT TEST RD
)@@G@@HERE  @G@@@@                                      . ALLOWS 'TRAILING' TRRE
)@@G@@ANS CHARS.  @E@@@@          TNE       A4,A5             . TEST IF UNMASKRF
)@@G@@ED =. @C@@@@          J         FIND5             . YES.    @F@@@@      RG
)@@G@@    TW        A8,A5             . IS CHAR ALPHA (LOWER).    @D@@@@      RH
)@@G@@    TNW       A13,A5            . OR UPPER.     @C@@@@          J       RI
)@@G@@  $+2               . YES.    @D@@@@          J         FIND8           RJ
)@@G@@  . NO, FAIL.     @E@@@@          AND       A5,CMSK           . CASE INDRK
)@@G@@EP IF REQ.  @C@@@@          AND       A4,CMSK           . LOWER.  @B@@@@RL
)@@G@@          TE        A5,A6             .   @ @@@@          J         FINDRM
)@@G@@8     @]@@@@FIND5     . @C@@@@          TLEM      A2,COUNT          . ATRN
)@@G@@ END. @ @@@@          J         FIND4     @E@@@@          TZ        NOTFRO
)@@G@@LG            . TEST IF .NOT. SET.  @F@@@@          J         FIND2     RP
)@@G@@        . YES, TREAT AS .NOT. FOUND.@#@@@@FIND6     . FOUND.@C@@@@      RQ
)@@G@@    L,U       A0,1              . GET 1.  @E@@@@          A         A0,FRR
)@@G@@FAIL          . INCREMENT COUNTER.  @D@@@@          S         A0,FFAIL  RS
)@@G@@        . SET FAIL FLAG.@F@@@@          TZ        PTFLG             . ISRT
)@@G@@ THIS PRINT TO FIND.    @D@@@@          J         FIND7             . YERU
)@@G@@S, END.     @ @@@@          TZ        BRIEF2    @ @@@@          LMJ     RV
)@@G@@  X10,TYPOUT@D@@@@          TNZ       LCFLG             . IS IT FC?     RW
)@@G@@@C@@@@          J         FIND7             . END.    @D@@@@          TZRX
)@@G@@        FLDFLG            . TEST FCD FLAG.@F@@@@          TNZ       LCFLRY
)@@G@@G             . DEL HERE IF 'D' AND 'C'.  @D@@@@          J         FINDRZ
)@@G@@2             . NOT DELETING. @D@@@@          LMJ       X10,DLSET       SA
)@@G@@  . DELETE LINE.  @D@@@@          J         FIND2             . NO IMAGESB
)@@G@@.     @B@@@@          J         FIND2             .   @]@@@@FIND7     . SC
)@@G@@@E@@@@          JGD       X7,FIND2          . LOOP IF REPEAT SET. @D@@@@SD
)@@G@@          J         NXRQ              . FINAL END.    @C@@@@FIND8     . SE
)@@G@@MATCH FAILED, TEST IF .NOT. SET.    @C@@@@          TNZ       NOTFLG    SF
)@@G@@        . SET ?   @D@@@@          J         FIND2             . NO, FAILSG
)@@G@@ IT.  @E@@@@          J         FIND6             . YES, TREAT AS MATCH.SH
)@@G@@@A@@@@FIND9     . ENTRY FOR END OF SCAN.. @D@@@@          LMJ       X9,LSI
)@@G@@OC12          . PRINT IT.     @B@@@@          J         FIND7           SJ
)@@G@@  .   @]@@@@/         . @[@@@@.     @F@@@@.         THIS CODE HANDLES ALSK
)@@G@@L FORMS OF THE 'LOCATE' COMMAND.    @B@@@@.         THERE ARE: L, LC, LPSL
)@@G@@, LS, LCD.  @[@@@@.     @ @@@@LOC1*     . 'L' COMMAND ENTRY.@E@@@@      SM
)@@G@@    SZ        LFAIL             . CLEAR FAIL FLAG.    @E@@@@          LMSN
)@@G@@J       X9,LFMOD          . SETUP ANY SUBFIELDS.@D@@@@          S       SO
)@@G@@  A10,CSTRT         . STORE IT.     @E@@@@          LMJ       X9,LFCHK  SP
)@@G@@        . CHECK ON IMAGE.     @E@@@@          LMJ       X9,LFCOP        SQ
)@@G@@  . COPY IF ANY PRESENT.@E@@@@          TZ        LSFLG             . TESR
)@@G@@ST FOR 'S' MOD.   @E@@@@          J         LOC3              . ENTER BESS
)@@G@@LOW W/R.    @^@@@@LOC1A     . **TEMP**    @D@@@@          L         X7,RST
)@@G@@PTK           . LOAD REPEAT.  @E@@@@          L         X8,NLIMT        SU
)@@G@@  . GET SCAN LIMIT.     @]@@@@LOC2      . @F@@@@          SZ        LLCNSV
)@@G@@              . CLEAR COL OF LOC POINTER. @D@@@@          TZ        LSFLSW
)@@G@@G             . IS IT 'LS'?   @E@@@@          J         NXRQ            SX
)@@G@@  . YES, EXIT HERE.     @A@@@@LOC3      . BYPASS FOR 'S' MOD.     @G@@@@SY
)@@G@@          LMJ       X9,NEXTIM         . GET, PRINT, DEL NEXT IMAGE.     SZ
)@@G@@@E@@@@          J         LOC14             . END OF SCAN RETURN. @E@@@@TA
)@@G@@          ON        SNOOP             . ONLY IF SNOOPY ON.  @G@@@@      TB
)@@G@@    TZ        NLIMT             . USE LINE SCAN LIMIT TO TURN ON. @D@@@@TC
)@@G@@          SLJ       TON$              . START SNOOP.  @D@@@@          OFTD
)@@G@@F       SNOOP             . END OF SNOOPY.@ @@@@          LA        A5,LTE
)@@G@@ENGTH @F@@@@          TG        A5,CEND           . TEST IF CEND SHORTERTF
)@@G@@.     @H@@@@          L         A5,CEND           . SET TO CEND. 'L' SCATG
)@@G@@N IS NOW DEF TO BE@C@@@@          . BETWEEN LCOLP AND CEND (INCLUSIVE). TH
)@@G@@@F@@@@          TG        A5,CSTRT          . TEST IF LINE TOO SHORT.   TI
)@@G@@@C@@@@          J         $+2               . NO.     @D@@@@          J TJ
)@@G@@        LOC13             . YES, FAIL.    @D@@@@          A         A5,(TK
)@@G@@1,1)          . SET INCR +1.  @E@@@@          L         A10,TRCHF       TL
)@@G@@  . GET TRANS CHAR.     @E@@@@          L         A0,EDCT           . SETM
)@@G@@T UP EDIT81 REG.  @E@@@@          A         A0,(1,1)          . +1 AND STN
)@@G@@ET INCR.    @E@@@@          L         A2,(1,0)          . SET IMAG80 POITO
)@@G@@NTER. @D@@@@          A         A2,CSTRT          . ADD OFFSET.   @E@@@@TP
)@@G@@          L         R2,(0777,0)       . LOAD MASK FOR Q2.   @E@@@@      TQ
)@@G@@    DL        A8,UAPL           . LOAD ALPHA RANGES.  @C@@@@          DLTR
)@@G@@        A13,UAPU          . UPPER.  @D@@@@          L         A6,COUNT  TS
)@@G@@        . END TEST.     @F@@@@          AU        A6,(1,0)          . A7TT
)@@G@@ = OFF END OF EDIT80.   @G@@@@          AN        A6,EDCT           . A6TU
)@@G@@ = LENGTH OF EDIT80 STRING+1. @F@@@@          AN,U      A6,1            TV
)@@G@@  . SET TO LENGTH OF EDIT STR.@D@@@@          TE        A10,EDIT80,A0   TW
)@@G@@  . IS FIRST TRAN.@E@@@@          J         LOC4              . NO, SKIPTX
)@@G@@ SEARCH.    @E@@@@          L         R1,A6             . GET IN RPT REGTY
)@@G@@.     @D@@@@          LSSL      A10,18            . SHIFT TO Q2.  @E@@@@TZ
)@@G@@          MSNE      A10,AREA,*A0      . LOOK FOR FIRST.     @F@@@@      UA
)@@G@@    J         LOC9              . NO NON-TRANS -> FOUND.    @F@@@@      UB
)@@G@@    AN,U      A0,1              . BACK UP TO NON TRANS.     @F@@@@      UC
)@@G@@    AN        A6,R1             . # OF LEADING TRAN CHARS.  @C@@@@      UD
)@@G@@    AN,U      A6,1              . LESS 1. @F@@@@          A         A2,AUE
)@@G@@6             . ADD TO IMAGE START COL.   @E@@@@          L         A6,RUF
)@@G@@1             . GET REMAINDER IN A6.@B@@@@LOC4      . ENTRY FROM BY PASSUG
)@@G@@ OF SEARCH. @D@@@@          A         A6,(1,1)          . SET INCR.     UH
)@@G@@@E@@@@          TLE       A5,A6             . TEST FOR EDIT>IMAGE.@D@@@@UI
)@@G@@          J         LOC13             . YES, FAIL.    @F@@@@          L UJ
)@@G@@        A6,A5             . SAVE (1,LENGTH+1) IN A6.  @C@@@@          L UK
)@@G@@        X10,A0            . SAVE A0.@D@@@@          L         A3,CMSK   UL
)@@G@@        . GET MASK.     @C@@@@          LSSL      A3,9              . TOUM
)@@G@@ Q3.  @D@@@@          L         R3,A3             . SAVE IN R3.   @E@@@@UN
)@@G@@          L,U       R4,0777000        . GET FULL MASK IN R4.@E@@@@      UO
)@@G@@    AN,U      A5,1              . SET TO (1,LENGTH).  @C@@@@          L UP
)@@G@@        R5,A5             . MOVE.   @^@@@@LOC5      . REENTRY.    @D@@@@UQ
)@@G@@          L         A4,R5             . GET IN A4.    @F@@@@          ANUR
)@@G@@U       A4,A2             . COMPUTE REMAINING LENGTH. @F@@@@          L US
)@@G@@        A3,AREA,*A0       . GET NEXT EDIT80 CHAR.     @C@@@@          SSUT
)@@G@@L       A3,9              . LINE UP.@E@@@@          L         R2,R4     UU
)@@G@@        . LOAD FULL MASK.     @D@@@@          TW        A8,EDIT81,A0    UV
)@@G@@  . IS CHAR ALPHA.@E@@@@          TNW       A13,EDIT81,A0     . UPPER ORUW
)@@G@@ LOWER.     @E@@@@          L         R2,R3             . YES, GET ALPHAUX
)@@G@@ MASK.@E@@@@          L         R1,A5             . REMAINDER OF IMAGE. UY
)@@G@@@D@@@@          MSE       A3,AREA,*A2       . LOOK FOR IT.  @F@@@@      UZ
)@@G@@    J         LOC13             . CHAR NOWHERE -> FAIL.     @E@@@@      VA
)@@G@@    S         A2,LLCN           . SET COL # OF FIND.  @ @@@@LOC6      . VB
)@@G@@REENTRY ON TRANS. @E@@@@          TG        A0,A7             . OFF END VC
)@@G@@OF EDIT80.  @E@@@@          J         LOC9              . YES, MATCH FOUVD
)@@G@@ND.   @D@@@@          L         A4,EDIT80,*A0     . GET NEXT.     @A@@@@VE
)@@G@@LOC7      . ENTRY IF ' ' IN IMAGE.  @F@@@@          L         A3,IMAG80,VF
)@@G@@*A2     . AND MATCHING IMAGE CHAR.  @E@@@@          TNE       A4,TRCHF  VG
)@@G@@        . LOOK FOR TRANS.     @D@@@@          J         LOC6            VH
)@@G@@  . YES, LOOP.    @E@@@@          TG        A2,A6             . TEST FORVI
)@@G@@ OFF END.   @D@@@@          J         LOC13             . YES, FAIL.    VJ
)@@G@@@E@@@@          TNE,U     A3,' '            . TEST FOR BLANKS.    @C@@@@VK
)@@G@@          J         LOC7              . YES.    @D@@@@          TNE     VL
)@@G@@  A3,A4             . TEST UNMASKED.@C@@@@          J         LOC6      VM
)@@G@@        . OK.     @E@@@@          TW        A8,A3             . TEST FORVN
)@@G@@ ALPHA.     @B@@@@          TNW       A13,A3            .   @D@@@@      VO
)@@G@@    J         $+2               . YES, MASK.    @C@@@@          J       VP
)@@G@@  LOC8              . NO, OUT.@C@@@@          AND       A4,CMSK         VQ
)@@G@@  . MASK.   @C@@@@          AND       A3,CMSK           .  ''     @C@@@@VR
)@@G@@          TNE       A4,A5             . COMPARE.@C@@@@          J       VS
)@@G@@  LOC6              . NEXT.   @A@@@@LOC8      . NO MASK, CHAR NOT =.    VT
)@@G@@@E@@@@          L         A0,X10            . RESET POINTERS.     @G@@@@VU
)@@G@@          L         A2,LLCN           . A0 SET BACK, A2 = PREVIOUS A2+1 VV
)@@G@@@C@@@@          J         LOC5              . LOOP.   @^@@@@LOC9      . VW
)@@G@@MATCH FOUND.@D@@@@          SZ,H1     LLCN              . CLEAR H1.     VX
)@@G@@@E@@@@          TZ        NOTFLG            . TEST IF .NOT. SET.  @F@@@@VY
)@@G@@          J         LOC2              . YES, TREAT AS NOT FOUND.  @]@@@@VZ
)@@G@@LOC10    .  @C@@@@          L,U       A0,1              . GET 1.  @E@@@@WA
)@@G@@          A         A0,LFAIL          . INCREMENT COUNTER.  @D@@@@      WB
)@@G@@    S         A0,LFAIL          . SET FAIL FLAG.@F@@@@          TZ      WC
)@@G@@  PTFLG             . IN PRINT TO LOC MODE?     @D@@@@          J       WD

)@@G@@        . YES, TREAT AS EQUAL.@E@@@@          TW        A8,A5           GA

)@@G@@@D@@@@          J         $+2               . YES IT IS.    @D@@@@      GC
)@@G@@    J         RESTAR1           . NO. FAIL.     @C@@@@          AND     GD
)@@G@@  A5,CMSK           . MASK.   @C@@@@          AND       A4,CMSK         GE
)@@G@@  . BOTH.   @C@@@@          TNE       A5,A6             . TEST.   @D@@@@GF
)@@G@@          J         SLINE1A           . MASKED ARE =. @^@@@@RESTAR1   . GG
)@@G@@NOT ALPHA.  @G@@@@          TNZ       PRTEST            . ALREADY CHANGEGH
)@@G@@D. NO, SET COL.   @D@@@@          S,H2      X7,CLCN           . SET STARGI
)@@G@@T COL.@ @@@@          TLEM      A1,LIMIT  @E@@@@          J         SLINGJ
)@@G@@E             . YES,CONTINUE SEARCH @G@@@@          TZ        PRTEST    GK
)@@G@@        . NON-ZERO MEANS LINE WAS CHANGED @ @@@@          J         CHDOGL
)@@G@@NE    @]@@@@NOCHAN    . @E@@@@          SZ        CLCN              . CLGM
)@@G@@EAR COL POINTER.  @E@@@@          TNZ       NFLG              . IS 'N' FGN
)@@G@@ORM IN USE? @C@@@@          JZ        A10,CXEND         . EXIT.   @F@@@@GO
)@@G@@          LMJ       X10,WRB           . WRITE OUT CURRENT IMAGE.  @D@@@@GP
)@@G@@          LMJ       X10,READ          . GET NEXT.     @D@@@@          J GQ
)@@G@@        EOF               . EOF RETURN.   @E@@@@          LMJ       X10,GR
)@@G@@DECOD1        . DECODE THE IMAGE.   @D@@@@          TZ        NFLG      GS
)@@G@@        . IS 'N' ON.    @C@@@@          J         GFOUND            . YEGT
)@@G@@S     @C@@@@          JGD       A10,GFOUND        . NO.     @B@@@@      GU
)@@G@@    J         CXEND             .   @]@@@@SFOUND    . @D@@@@          L,GV
)@@G@@U       A4,' '            . GET BLANK.    @]@@@@SFOUND1   . @F@@@@      GW
)@@G@@    TNE       A1,A2             . MOVE BEGINNING OF LINE TO @E@@@@      GX
)@@G@@    J         REPLAC            . ALTERNATE BUFFER    @D@@@@          L GY
)@@G@@        A5,IMAG80,A2      . GET CHAR.     @C@@@@          S         A4,CGZ
)@@G@@HAN80,A3      . CLEAR.  @E@@@@          TLEM      A2,LENGTH         . SKHA
)@@G@@IP IF OFF END.    @D@@@@          S         A5,CHAN80,A3      . SET CHARHB
)@@G@@.     @C@@@@          TLEM      A3,SAVE21         .  SAVE2-1@C@@@@      HC
)@@G@@    J         SFOUND1           . LOOP.   @E@@@@          J         TT  HD
)@@G@@              . NORMAL END OF MOVE. @ @@@@REPLAC    . REPLACE STRING.   HE
)@@G@@@F@@@@          L,Q2      A0,STR            . CHECK TO SEE IF STRING IS HF
)@@G@@@^@@@@REPLAC1   . REENTRY.    @E@@@@          A,U       A0,1            HG
)@@G@@  . ALREADY REPLACED ?  @G@@@@          TNE,Q3    A0,STR            . TEHH
)@@G@@ST IF LAST DELIM REACHED.     @C@@@@          J         REDONE          HI
)@@G@@  . YES     @G@@@@          L         A5,EDIT80,A0      . NO,MOVE NEXT CHJ
)@@G@@HAR OF 2ND STRING @E@@@@          S         A5,CHAN80,A3      . TO CHAN8HK
)@@G@@0 BUFFER.   @C@@@@          TLEM      A3,SAVE21         .  SAVE2-1@F@@@@HL
)@@G@@          J         REPLAC1           . LOOP UNTIL END OF STRING. @C@@@@HM
)@@G@@          A,U       A0,1              . INCR.   @F@@@@          TE,Q3   HN
)@@G@@  A0,STR            . TEST IF COMPLETED MOVE.   @C@@@@          J       HO
)@@G@@  TT1               . NO.     @H@@@@          TNZ       GLOBAL          HP
)@@G@@  . FORCE TRUNCATION WARNING IF GLOBAL.   @E@@@@          J         TT  HQ
)@@G@@              . YES, NORMAL EXIT.   @]@@@@REDONE    . @C@@@@          L,HR
)@@G@@U       A0,1              . GET 1.  @F@@@@          S         A0,NOCHGF HS
)@@G@@        . SET CHANGED THIS PASS.    @E@@@@          A         A0,CFAIL  HT
)@@G@@        . INCREMENT COUNTER.  @G@@@@          S         A0,CFAIL        HU
)@@G@@  . SET LOGIC FLAG FOR THIS USE.    @F@@@@          S         A0,PRTEST HV
)@@G@@        . NON-0 MEANS LINE CHANGED. @E@@@@          L         A0,X7     HW
)@@G@@        . RESET REGISTERS.    @B@@@@          L         A1,X7           HX
)@@G@@  .   @B@@@@          ANA,U     A1,1              .   @B@@@@          L HY
)@@G@@        A2,X7             .   @G@@@@          TZ        GLOBAL          HZ
)@@G@@  . IS REST OF LINE TO BE CHANGED ? @B@@@@          J         RESTAR1   IA
)@@G@@        .   @]@@@@CHDONE    . @C@@@@          L         A4,CLCN         IB
)@@G@@  . GET COL.@C@@@@          A,U       A4,1              . INCR.   @C@@@@IC
)@@G@@          S         A4,CLCN           . SET.    @E@@@@          L       ID
)@@G@@  A1,LENGTH         . GET IMAGE LENGTH.   @C@@@@          AN,U      A1,1IE
)@@G@@              . LESS 1. @F@@@@          TG        A1,SAVE21         . TEIF
)@@G@@ST IF AT LENGTH LIMIT.  @E@@@@          L         A1,SAVE21         . YEIG
)@@G@@S, SET TO LIMIT-1.@D@@@@          LXI,U     A1,1              . SET INCRIH
)@@G@@.     @E@@@@          L         A2,SAVE21         . GET CURRENT SAVE21. II
)@@G@@@E@@@@          A         A2,(1,1)          . SET INCR AND ADD 1. @]@@@@IJ
)@@G@@MOVE1     . @B@@@@          TLE       A1,A0             .   @B@@@@      IK
)@@G@@    J         TT                .   @D@@@@          L         A5,IMAG80,IL
)@@G@@*A0     . GET NEXT CHAR.@E@@@@          TG        A3,A2             . TEIM
)@@G@@ST IF TOO LONG.   @G@@@@          J         MOVE11            . YES, BUTIN
)@@G@@ LOOK FOR TRUNCATION.   @F@@@@          TNG       A3,(1,132)        . DOIO
)@@G@@ NOT STORE OFF END.     @B@@@@          SA        A5,CHAN80,*A3     .   IP
)@@G@@@B@@@@          J         MOVE1             .   @]@@@@MOVE11    . @B@@@@IQ
)@@G@@          TNE,U     A5,' '            .   @B@@@@          J         MOVEIR
)@@G@@1             .   @B@@@@          A,U       A3,1              .   @]@@@@IS
)@@G@@TT1       . @E@@@@          TNZ       BRIEF2            . IN BRIEF MODE IT
)@@G@@?     @D@@@@          J         TT3               . YES, SKIP     @B@@@@IU
)@@G@@          TZ        NFLG              .   @B@@@@          J         TT2 IV
)@@G@@              .   @F@@@@          TNZ       A10               . ARE WE SIW
)@@G@@CANNING THROUGH.  @G@@@@          JNZ       A7,TT3            . SCANNINGIX
)@@G@@ AND NOT AT END OF REPT.@]@@@@TT2       . @D@@@@          PRINT     E18,IY
)@@G@@L18,2,1       . PRINT WARNING.@B@@@@TT3       . ENTRY FROM TRUNCATION COIZ
)@@G@@DE.   @D@@@@          L,U       A5,' '            . GET BLANK.    @E@@@@JA
)@@G@@          L         A1,LENGTH         . GET CURRENT LENGTH. @E@@@@      JB
)@@G@@    TG        A1,SAVE21         .  CHANGED TO SAVE2-1 @ @@@@          J JC
)@@G@@        MOVE2     @ @@@@          ANA       A3,(1,1)  @D@@@@          S,JD
)@@G@@H2      A3,LENGTH         . SET SHORTER.  @D@@@@          AN,U      A3,1JE
)@@G@@              . BACK UP AGAIN.@C@@@@          J         MOVE3           JF
)@@G@@  . SET L   @^@@@@TT        . NORMAL END. @C@@@@          L,U       A5,'JG
)@@G@@ '            . BLNK.   @B@@@@          L         A1,LENGTH         .   JH
)@@G@@@H@@@@          TG        A1,SAVE21         . THIS CODE ALMOST DUPS CODEJI
)@@G@@ ABOVE.     @B@@@@          J         MOVE2             .   @E@@@@      JJ
)@@G@@    S,H2      A3,LENGTH         . SET RIGHT LENGTH.   @C@@@@          ANJK
)@@G@@A       A3,(1,1)          . BACK 1. @B@@@@          J         MOVE3     JL
)@@G@@        .   @A@@@@MOVE2     . CLEAR END OF CHANGE BUF.@F@@@@          TNJM
)@@G@@G       A3,(1,132)        . DO NOT STORE OFF END.     @A@@@@          S JN
)@@G@@        A5,CHAN80,A3    @C@@@@          TLEM      A3,SAVE21         . SAJO
)@@G@@VE21  @ @@@@          J         MOVE2     @D@@@@          L         A3,SJP
)@@G@@AVE21         .   SAVE2-1     @]@@@@MOVE3     . @E@@@@          L       JQ
)@@G@@  A5,CHAN80,A3      . GET NEXT CHANG CHAR.@E@@@@          S         A5,IJR
)@@G@@MAG80,A3      . SET IT IN IMAG80.   @C@@@@          JGD       A3,MOVE3  JS
)@@G@@        . LOOP.   @D@@@@          L,U       A0,1              . GET FLAGJT
)@@G@@.     @F@@@@          S         A0,NOCHGF         . SET CHANGED THIS PASJU
)@@G@@S.    @D@@@@          TZ        NFLG              . WAS NEXT SET. @C@@@@JV
)@@G@@          J         MOVE4             . YES.    @D@@@@          TNZ     JW
)@@G@@  A10               . SCANNING?     @E@@@@          JGD       A7,GFOUND JX
)@@G@@        . LOOP ON REPEAT.     @B@@@@MOVE4     . REENTER FOR END OF REPEAJY
)@@G@@T.    @E@@@@          SNA       RC,DC1            . IMAGE DELETED BY ED JZ
)@@G@@@E@@@@          LMJ       X10,WRB           . WRITE THE IMAGE OUT.@E@@@@KA
)@@G@@          SNA       RC,AC1            . IMAGE ADDED BY ED   @E@@@@      KB
)@@G@@    LMJ       X10,PACK          . PACK CURRENT IMAGE. @G@@@@          LMKC
)@@G@@J       X10,DECOD1        . RECONVERT TO SET FCOLP+LENGTH.  @ @@@@      KD
)@@G@@    TZ        BRIEF2    @D@@@@          LMJ       X10,TYPOUT        . PRKE
)@@G@@INT CURRENT.@H@@@@          TNZ       NFLG              . MUST READ NEXTKF
)@@G@@ IF 'N' AND A7.NE.0     @B@@@@          J         MOVE5             .   KG
)@@G@@@B@@@@          JZ        A7,CXEND2         .   @D@@@@          J       KH
)@@G@@  MOVE6             . READ NEXT.    @]@@@@MOVE5     . @ @@@@          JZKI
)@@G@@        A10,CXEND2@]@@@@MOVE6     . @E@@@@          LMJ       X10,WRB   KJ

)@@G@@  . READ IN NEXT IMAGE. @D@@@@          J         EOF               . EOKL
)@@G@@F RETURN.   @E@@@@          LMJ       X10,DECOD1        . DECODE THE IMAKM
)@@G@@GE.   @E@@@@          TZ        NFLG              . SKIP IF 'N' SET.    KN
)@@G@@@B@@@@          J         CXEND2            .   @ @@@@          JGD     KO
)@@G@@  A10,GFOUND@D@@@@          . A10 SHOULD NEVER BE ZERO AT ABOVE JGD.    KP
)@@G@@@B@@@@CXEND     . COMMON EXIT AND REPEAT TEST.  @C@@@@          JGD     KQ
)@@G@@  A7,GFOUND         . LOOP.   @E@@@@          TZ        PRTEST          KR
)@@G@@  . DID CURRENT SUCCEED.@C@@@@          J         MOVE4             . YEKS
)@@G@@S.    @C@@@@          J         NXRQ              . NO.     @ @@@@CXEND2KT
)@@G@@    . FINAL EXIT TEST.  @E@@@@          JGD       A7,GFOUND         . LOKU
)@@G@@OP ONLY ON RPT.   @B@@@@          J         NXRQ              .   @A@@@@KV
)@@G@@UAPL      +0100     . ALPHA RANGES. @ @@@@          +0132     . UPPER.  KW
)@@G@@@ @@@@UAPU      +0140     . LOWER.  @^@@@@          +0172     .   @^@@@@KX
)@@G@@          END       .   ___     A3,(1,132)        . DO NOT STORE OFF ENDKY
)@@G@@.     @A@@@@          S         A5,CHAN80,A3    @C@@@@          TLEM    KZ
)@@G@@  A3,SAVE21         . SA*[@@@@*SDFF*@^@@@@          AXR$      .   @^@@@@LA
)@@G@@          EDPC      .   @#@@@@$(1)      . IBANK.@^@@@@          LIT     LB
)@@G@@.     @ @@@@          ASCII   . SET ASCII.@E@@@@          . THIS ROUTINELC
)@@G@@ HANDLES FILE INPUT USING SDFI.     @C@@@@          . ITS ENTRY POINT ISLD
)@@G@@ : LMJ  X10,READ .@]@@@@          . @G@@@@          . HOWEVER, NOTE THATLE
)@@G@@ THE ROUTINE 'FILE' DOES NOT USE 'READ'.  @A@@@@          . IT USES SDFILF
)@@G@@ DIRECTLY.  @]@@@@          . @E@@@@SNOOP     EQU       0               LG
)@@G@@  . SNOOPY ON/OFF FLAG. @^@@@@P         PROC      .   @^@@@@SNPTX*    NALH
)@@G@@ME      .   @B@@@@          ON        SNOOP             .   @C@@@@      LI
)@@G@@    S         A0,SNPKT+2        . SAVE.   @D@@@@          L,U       A0,CLJ

)@@G@@        .   @^@@@@          END       .   @]@@@@READ*     . @E@@@@      LO

)@@G@@              . ALREADY AT EOF ?    @D@@@@          J         0,X10     LT

)@@G@@U       A2,PGLIN          .   @B@@@@          LMJ       X11,FDASC       PZ
)@@G@@  .   @#@@@@GETSP23        .  @D@@@@          TE,U      A0,050          QA
)@@G@@  . IS IT LABEL.  @C@@@@          J         GETSP             . NO.     QB
)@@G@@@F@@@@          L         A0,FCIMG          . CHECK IF EMBEDDED TYPE 050QC
)@@G@@@D@@@@          TNE       A0,EDSDF          . AND*SDFF*     @C@@@@      QD
)@@G@@    J         READI             . SKIP IT.@E@@@@          L,S6      A0,IQE
)@@G@@CW            . GET ASCII SWITCH.   @E@@@@          TZ        PS1ALL    QF
)@@G@@        . SKIP IF NOT PASS1.  @C@@@@          J         GETSP231        QG
)@@G@@  . ALREADY.@E@@@@          TZ        ADSAVE            . SET ON PASS 1 QH
)@@G@@ONLY. @C@@@@          S         A0,ASCIN          . SET IT. @]@@@@GETSP2QI
)@@G@@31  . @D@@@@          DL        A0,IMAGE          . CHECK FOR     @E@@@@QJ
)@@G@@          TZ        TXTM              . TEST FOR TEXT MODE. @B@@@@      QK
)@@G@@    DL        A0,IMTMP          .   @F@@@@          TZ        PRFIL     QL
)@@G@@        . HAS PRINTFILE BEEN SET,   @C@@@@          J         READI     QM
)@@G@@        . YES     @C@@@@          S         A0,FCIMG          . SET IT  QN
)@@G@@@D@@@@          TNE       A0,EDSDF          . IS IT *SDFF*  @C@@@@      QO
)@@G@@    J         READI             . YES     @E@@@@          L,S2      A2,IQP
)@@G@@CW            . GET IMAGE LENGTH    @D@@@@          TG,U      A2,12     QQ
)@@G@@        . TOO BIG ?     @D@@@@          L,U       A2,12             . YEQR
)@@G@@S, TRUNCATE.@H@@@@          TZ,S1     IMAGE             . TRY S1 TO CATCQS
)@@G@@H FV AND DIRECT ACCESS. @B@@@@          J         GETSP24           . NOQT
)@@G@@@F@@@@          L         A0,( P 1,0,FORLB) . SET UP FORTRAN OR D/A.    QU
)@@G@@@D@@@@          L         A1,A2             . GET LENGTH.   @C@@@@      QV
)@@G@@    LSSL      A1,18             . IN S3.  @C@@@@          A         A0,AQW
)@@G@@1             . ADD IN. @E@@@@          ER        PRINT$            . PRQX
)@@G@@INT FORTRAN MSG.  @D@@@@          L,U       A0,1              . GET FLAGQY
)@@G@@.     @H@@@@          S         A0,FORF           . SET TO TELL READ TO QZ
)@@G@@CLEAR SPACING.    @F@@@@          TNE,U     A2,3              . IF A2=3 RA
)@@G@@IS DIRECT ACCESS. @E@@@@          S         A0,ROPT           . SO SET RRB
)@@G@@EAD ONLY.   @A@@@@GETSP24   . ENTRY IF NOT FORTRAN.   @E@@@@          L RC
)@@G@@        A0,ICW            . GET IN CONTROL WORD.@D@@@@          S       RD
)@@G@@  A0,E16L           . SAVE LENGTH.  @D@@@@          L         R1,A2     RE
)@@G@@        . GET COUNT.    @C@@@@          MOVE      IMAGE,E16+2       . CORF
)@@G@@PY.   @F@@@@          TZ        FORF              . TEST IF FORTRAN TYPERG
)@@G@@S.    @G@@@@          J         GETSP25           . YES, BYPASS PRINT OFRH
)@@G@@ LABEL.     @D@@@@          L,S2      A0,ICW            . GET LENGTH    RI
)@@G@@@E@@@@          A,U       A0,2              . ADD TWO FOR HEADER  @D@@@@RJ
)@@G@@          TE,U      A0,035            . TEST FOR FTN. @E@@@@          J RK
)@@G@@        NOTFTN1           . IF FTN LENGTH=033.  @D@@@@          DL      RL
)@@G@@  A1,FTNT1          . GET WORD1+2.  @E@@@@          DS        A1,E16    RM
)@@G@@        . SET 'FTN UNIT #:'.  @D@@@@          DL        A1,FTNT2        RN
)@@G@@  . GET DATE PART.@C@@@@          DS        A1,E16+4          . SET.    RO
)@@G@@@E@@@@          L,U       A1,1              . SET FOR FLAG TO     @F@@@@RP
)@@G@@          S         A1,FORF           . CONTROL LINE SPACING.     @D@@@@RQ
)@@G@@          L,U       A0,7              . GET LENGTH.   @C@@@@NOTFTN1   . RR
)@@G@@ENTRY IF NOT FTN FORMATTED FILE.    @C@@@@          L         A1,A0     RS
)@@G@@        . SAVE AO.@F@@@@          TNE,U     A0,013            . IS IT LERT
)@@G@@VEL 32 FILE.(11+2)@F@@@@          L,U       A0,6              . IF LEVELRU
)@@G@@ 32, RESET TO 6.  @C@@@@          LSSL      A0,18             . SHIFT.  RV
)@@G@@@A@@@@          AA        A0,( P 1,0,E16) @F@@@@          TZ        PRFIRW
)@@G@@L             . IS IT PRINTFILE MODE?     @D@@@@          J         GETSRX
)@@G@@P27           . YES, SKIP MSG.@F@@@@          TZ        BRIEF2          RY
)@@G@@  . NOT IF IN BRIEF MODE.     @D@@@@          ER        PRINT$          RZ
)@@G@@  . PRINT IT.     @E@@@@          TE,U      A1,013            . WAS LENGSA
)@@G@@TH 11 (L32).@F@@@@          J         GETSP25           . NO, DONE IF NOSB
)@@G@@T LEVEL32.  @D@@@@          E$DIT     ETAB              . OPEN EDIT.    SC
)@@G@@@D@@@@          E$COPY    10,FTNT2          . COPY IN DATE: @D@@@@      SD
)@@G@@    E$DAY2    IMAGE+4           . SET DATE.     @C@@@@          E$SKIP  SE
)@@G@@  1                 . SPACE 1.@D@@@@          E$TIME    IMAGE+4         SF
)@@G@@  . SET TIME.     @ @@@@          E$DITX    . CLOSE.  @C@@@@          L SG
)@@G@@        A0,( P 1,5,IMBUF) . PRINT   @C@@@@          ER        PRINT$    SH
)@@G@@        . TDATE$. @]@@@@GETSP25   . @E@@@@          TZ        DOPT      SI
)@@G@@        . DATAFILE OR D-OPT ? @G@@@@          J         GETSP26         SJ
)@@G@@  . SKIP ERROR MESSAGE AND EXIT.    @E@@@@          PRINT     E17,L17,2,SK
)@@G@@1       . TELL USER BAD NEWS. @E@@@@          S         A0,SOPT         SL
)@@G@@  . SET S-OPT AND GO ON.@]@@@@GETSP26   . @E@@@@          TZ        COPTSM
)@@G@@              . TREAT IT AS SDFF ?  @C@@@@          J         GETSP27   SN
)@@G@@        . YES.    @E@@@@          TZ        FORF              . IS IT FOSO
)@@G@@RTRAN TYPE. @C@@@@          J         GETSP26A          . YES.    @E@@@@SP
)@@G@@          L,S2      A1,SPACEM         . GET SPACE BIAS.     @D@@@@      SQ
)@@G@@    TZ        A1                . ALREADY 0?    @C@@@@          AN,U    SR
)@@G@@  A1,1              . LESS 1. @D@@@@          S,S2      A1,SPACEM       SS
)@@G@@  . RESET -1.     @ @@@@GETSP26A  . ENTRY IF FORT.    @D@@@@          L,ST
)@@G@@U       A0,1              . GET FLAG.     @F@@@@          S         A0,PSU
)@@G@@RFIL          . SET INPUT IS PRINTFILE.   @]@@@@GETSP27   . @G@@@@      SV
)@@G@@    J         READI             . DO NOT WRITE HEADERS INTO FILE. @]@@@@SW
)@@G@@GETSP     . @ @@@@          SX        X10,X10SAV@ @@@@          LMJ     SX
)@@G@@  X10,WRB   @D@@@@          LX        X10,X10SAV        . RELOAD X10    SY
)@@G@@@F@@@@          J         READI             . REENTER FOR NEXT IMAGE.   SZ
)@@G@@@[@@@@.     @[@@@@.     @]@@@@DECODE    . @E@@@@          TNZ       AC1 TA
)@@G@@              . IMAGE ADDED BY ED?  @F@@@@          AN,U      OLCT,1    TB
)@@G@@        . NO , DECR INPUT COUNT.    @D@@@@          TZ        LCT       TC
)@@G@@        . INCR IF 0.    @H@@@@          TNZ       DC1               . INTD
)@@G@@ CASE DELETIONS ARE BEING OUTPUT.   @F@@@@          A,U       LCT,1     TE
)@@G@@        . INCREMENT  LINE COUNT     @F@@@@          TZ        CINT      TF
)@@G@@        . GO TO DECODE IF INTERRUPT.@G@@@@          TZ        TXTM      TG
)@@G@@        . DO NOT GO INTO DECOD1 IF TM.    @C@@@@          J         1,X1TH
)@@G@@0             . RETURN. @]@@@@/         . @F@@@@. ROUTINE TO UNPACK LINETI
)@@G@@ FROM IMAGE INTO CHAR BUFFER: IMAG80.     @B@@@@DECOD1*   . ENTRY FOR DETJ
)@@G@@CODE W/O READ.    @E@@@@          L,U       A1,3              . CLEAR FITK
)@@G@@RST WORD.   @D@@@@          L,U       A3,' '            . TO BLANK.     TL
)@@G@@@E@@@@          S         A3,IMAG80,A1      . IN CASE OF 0 LENGTH.@B@@@@TM
)@@G@@          JGD       A1,$-1            .   @D@@@@          TNZ       IL  TN
)@@G@@              . TEST FOR 0.   @D@@@@          J         DEC3            TO
)@@G@@  . SKIP IF 0.    @F@@@@          SZ        LENGTH            . INIT LENTP
)@@G@@GTH IN CASE BLANK.@E@@@@          L         A0,(1,0)          . INITIALITQ
)@@G@@ZE REGS.    @C@@@@          L         A1,A0             . A1=A0   @D@@@@TR
)@@G@@          L         A2,(1,1)          . OFFSET A2.    @^@@@@DEC1      . TS
)@@G@@LOOP ENTRY. @ @@@@          EX        DEC2,*A0  @E@@@@          S       TT
)@@G@@  A3,IMAG80,*A1     . STORE CHARACTER     @E@@@@          J         DEC1TU
)@@G@@              . LOAD NEXT CHAR.     @]@@@@DEC2      . @B@@@@          LATV
)@@G@@,Q1     A3,IMAGE-1,A2     .   @B@@@@          LA,Q2     A3,IMAGE-1,A2   TW
)@@G@@  .   @B@@@@          LA,Q3     A3,IMAGE-1,A2     .   @B@@@@          LATX
)@@G@@,Q4     A3,IMAGE-1,A2     .   @B@@@@          J         $+1             TY
)@@G@@  .   @B@@@@          LA        A0,(1,0)          .   @G@@@@          TLTZ
)@@G@@EM      A2,IL             . DOES WORD COUNT=IMAGE LENGTH?   @C@@@@      UA
)@@G@@    J         DEC1              . NOT YET @F@@@@          AN        A1,(UB
)@@G@@1,1)          . SET BACK TO LAST CHAR.    @^@@@@DEC22     . LOOP ENTRY. UC
)@@G@@@D@@@@          L         A3,IMAG80,A1      . GET LAST CHAR.@D@@@@      UD
)@@G@@    TNE,U     A3,' '            . IS IT BLANK.  @E@@@@          JGD     UE
)@@G@@  A1,DEC22          . YES, BACK SCAN.     @D@@@@          A,U       A1,1UF
)@@G@@              . +1 FOR LENGTH.@C@@@@          S         A1,LENGTH       UG
)@@G@@  . SET IT. @F@@@@          TZ        A1                . WAS INPUT A BLUH
)@@G@@ANK LINE.   @D@@@@          J         DEC4              . YES, EXIT.    UI
)@@G@@@ @@@@DEC3      . HANDLE BLANK LINE.@F@@@@          L         A0,LCOLP  UJ
)@@G@@        . GET LEFT WINDOW MARGIN.   @C@@@@          A,U       A0,1      UK
)@@G@@        . +1.     @F@@@@          S         A0,LCOLC          . SET LEFTUL
)@@G@@ COL POINTER.     @D@@@@          S         A0,RCOLC          . SET RIGHUM
)@@G@@T TOO.@B@@@@          L,U       A0,1              .   @B@@@@          S UN
)@@G@@        A0,IL             .   @B@@@@          S         A0,LENGTH       UO
)@@G@@  .   @D@@@@          L         A0,ASCBL          . GET BLNK.     @C@@@@UP
)@@G@@          S         A0,IMAGE          . CLEAR.  @D@@@@          J       UQ
)@@G@@  DEC41             . COMMON EXIT.  @C@@@@          . SET LCOLC AND RCOLUR
)@@G@@C. LOGIC IS THAT  @D@@@@          . LCOLC IS FIRST NON-BLANK WITHIN WINDUS
)@@G@@OW    @D@@@@          . OR LEFT WINDOW BOUNDARY IF IMAGE SHORTER  @^@@@@UT
)@@G@@          . THAN WINDOW.@D@@@@          . RCOLC IS LAST NON-BLANK BEFOREUU
)@@G@@ WINDOW, OR @D@@@@          . WINDOW BOUNDARY ON RIGHT IF IMAGE STARTS  UV
)@@G@@@ @@@@          . BEYOND WINDOW.    @]@@@@DEC4*     . @F@@@@          L UW
)@@G@@        A1,LCOLP          . GET LEFT WINDOW MARGIN.   @C@@@@          AUUX
)@@G@@,U      A1,1              . +1.     @G@@@@          S         A2,LCOLC  UY
)@@G@@        . SET POINTERS TO LEFT MARGIN.    @C@@@@          S         A2,RUZ
)@@G@@COLC          . BOTH.   @D@@_@          L         A2,LENGTH         . GEVA
)@@G@@T LENGTH.   @G@@_@          TNE,U     A2,1              . TEST FOR =1 =>VB
)@@G@@ BLANK OR 1 CHAR. @H@@_@          J         DEC41             . CODE BELVC
)@@G@@OW WILL FAIL ON BLANK LINE.   @F@@@@          TG        A1,LENGTH       VD
)@@G@@  . IS LEFT WINDOW > LENGTH.  @C@@@@          J         DEC41           VE
)@@G@@  . YES.    @D@@@@          LXI,U     A1,1              . SET INCR.     VF
)@@G@@@E@@@@          L         A0,IMAG80,*A1     . GET FIRST CHAR.     @D@@@@VG
)@@G@@          TNE,U     A0,' '            . IS IT BLANK.  @D@@@@          J VH
)@@G@@        $-2               . YES, LOOP.    @D@@@@          AN        A1,(VI
)@@G@@1,0)          . REMOVE INCR.  @E@@@@          TG        A1,CEND         VJ
)@@G@@  . TEST IF OFF END.    @E@@@@          L         A1,CEND           . YEVK
)@@G@@S, GET MARGIN.    @E@@@@          S         A1,LCOLC          . SET LEFTVL
)@@G@@ POINTER.   @E@@@@          L         A1,CEND           . GET RIGHT MARGVM
)@@G@@IN.   @D@@@@          TG        A1,LENGTH         . IS LENGTH<=   @E@@@@VN
)@@G@@          L         A1,LENGTH         . GET IMAGE LENGTH.   @C@@@@      VO
)@@G@@    S         A1,RCOLC          . SET.    @]@@@@DEC41     . @F@@@@      VP
)@@G@@    TZ        CINT              . CHECK FOR INTERRUPT .     @G@@@@      VQ
)@@G@@    J         NXRQ              . GO TO NEXT IF INTERRUPT SET.    @D@@@@VR
)@@G@@          J         0,X10             . NORMAL RETURN.@B@@@@/         . VS
)@@G@@ROUTINE TO HANDLE TEXT MODE.  @F@@@@          . TEXT MODE WORKS ACCORDINVT
)@@G@@G TO THE FOLLOWING RULES:     @E@@@@          . 1. THE MODE IS SET, OR RVU
)@@G@@ESET, BY  'TX K <L>'    @F@@@@          . 2. EDQ ATTEMPTS TO GENERATE LIVV
)@@G@@NES WHICH ARE OF LENGTH @G@@@@          .    NEAR TO THE RIGHT MARGIN SEVW
)@@G@@T BY 'TX'. THIS IS DONE BY    @G@@@@          .    TRUNCATION, OR CONCATVX
)@@G@@INATION OF LINES. A LINE WHICH HAS  @G@@@@          .    A BLANK CHARACTVY
)@@G@@ER IN THE LEFT COLUMN (OR A NON-BLANK     @G@@@@          .    BEFORE THVZ
)@@G@@E LEFT COLUMN START) TERMINATES CONCATINATION.  @G@@@@          . 3. ENTWA
)@@G@@ERING TEXT MODE CAUSES THE IMAGE BUFFER TO BE CHANGED @G@@@@          . WB
)@@G@@   SO THAT IMAGES ARE READ FROM SDFI INTO 'IMTMP'. THEY     @G@@@@      WC
)@@G@@    .    ARE THEN COPIED INTO 'IMAGE' TO SATISFY THE LINE LENGTH  @ @@@@WD
)@@G@@          .    SPECIFICCATION.@F@@@@          .    NOTE THAT USE OF 'IMAWE
)@@G@@GE' MUST BE RESTORED WHEN TEXT@A@@@@          .    MODE IS TURNED OFF!! WF
)@@G@@@]@@@@          . @ @@@@TRED1     . ENTRY FROM READ.  @B@@@@          SNWG
)@@G@@PON     . TURN ON SNOOPY.     @D@@@@          S         X10,TRX10S      WH
)@@G@@  . SAVE LINK REG.@D@@@@          S         X9,R4             . SAVE X9,WI
)@@G@@ TOO. @F@@@@          L,U       A0,IMTMP          . SET CORRECT LINE ADDWJ
)@@G@@R.    @C@@@@          S,H2      A0,EDIN+8         . SET IT. @D@@@@      WK
)@@G@@    L,U       A0,1              . GET FLAG.     @F@@@@          S       WL
)@@G@@  A0,NOCHGF         . SET CHANGED THIS PASS.    @D@@@@          S       WM
)@@G@@  A0,CCHAR          . SET AT COL 1. @D@@@@          L         A4,LMAR   WN
)@@G@@        . GET LEFT COL. @G@@@@          LMJ       X11,BBIM          . BLWO
)@@G@@ANK LMAR OR LMARI FROM COL 1. @E@@@@          L         A0,LMAR         WP
)@@G@@  . SET CURR POINTER IN @D@@@@          TZ        LMARI             . IFWQ
)@@G@@ INDENT SET,@C@@@@          S         A0,CCHAR          . IMAGE.  @G@@@@WR
)@@G@@          TZ        PBIL              . TEST IF ANYTHING IN BUFFER.     WS
)@@G@@@C@@@@          J         COPT0             . YES.    @F@@@@          TZWT
)@@G@@        TXTMOFF           . IF TX TO BE TURNED OFF,   @E@@@@          J WU
)@@G@@        COPTE11           . DO NOT READ ANY NEW.@A@@@@          SNPOFF  WV
)@@G@@  . TURN OFF.     @E@@@@          LMJ       X10,READI         . NO, GET WW
)@@G@@A LINE.     @D@@@@          J         TRED3             . EOF EXIT.     WX
)@@G@@@A@@@@          SNPON     . ON SNOOPY.    @E@@@@          L         A0,AWY
)@@G@@SCBL          . GET A BLANK WORD.   @D@@@@          L         A1,IL     WZ
)@@G@@        . GET LENGTH.   @D@@@@          S         A0,IMTMP,A1       . SEXA
)@@G@@T BLANK.    @C@@@@          L,U       A0,1              . GET 1   @E@@@@XB
)@@G@@          S         A0,BCHAR          . SET IMTMP START.    @F@@@@      XC
)@@G@@    LMJ       X10,TRPAR         . SETUP PARAMETERS FOR IMAGE@D@@@@      XD
)@@G@@                                . IN IMTMP.     @E@@@@          L       XE
)@@G@@  A0,LMAR           . GET LEFT MARGIN.    @F@@@@          TNZ       CRSTXF
)@@G@@P             . DOES LINE STOP CONCAT.    @E@@@@          S         A0,CXG
)@@G@@CHAR          . NO, SET TO LMAR.    @E@@@@          L         A0,LCHAR  XH
)@@G@@        . TEST FOR BLANK LINE.@E@@@@          TE,U      A0,1            XI
)@@G@@  . LCHAR=1 -> BLANK.   @F@@@@          J         COPT1             . GOXJ
)@@G@@ TO TRUNC/CAT ROUTINE.  @B@@@@TRED2     . ENTRY FOR O/P OF BLANK LINE.  XK
)@@G@@@F@@@@          L,U       A0,4              . COPY 4 CHARS FOR BLANK.   XL
)@@G@@@C@@@@          S         A0,NCHAR          . SET     @F@@@@          L,XM
)@@G@@U       A0,1              . FORCE START TO COL 1.     @C@@@@          S XN
)@@G@@        A0,CCHAR          . SET.    @C@@@@          LMJ       X11,TRAP  XO
)@@G@@        . DO COPY.@E@@@@          SZ        PBIL              . SET IMTMXP
)@@G@@P EMPTY.    @D@@@@          J         COPTE             . NORMAL EXIT.  XQ
)@@G@@@ @@@@TRED3     . EOF HANDLING.     @A@@@@          SNPOFF    . SNOOPY OXR
)@@G@@FF.   @F@@@@          SZ        TXTM              . SHUT OFF TEXT MODE OXS
)@@G@@N EOF.@E@@@@          L,U       A0,IMAGE          . GET IMAGE ADDR.     XT
)@@G@@@C@@@@          S,H2      A0,EDIN+8         . SET IT. @C@@@@          L XU
)@@G@@        X10,TRX10S        . RELOAD. @D@@@@          L         X9,R4     XV
)@@G@@        . RELOAD X9.    @D@@@@          J         0,X10             . EOXW
)@@G@@F RETURN.   @A@@@@COPT0     . ENTRY IF PBIL .NE. 0    @E@@@@          L XX
)@@G@@        A0,LCHAR          . TEST FOR BLANK LINE.@F@@@@          TNE,U   XY
)@@G@@  A0,1              . LCHAR.EQ.1 -> BLANK LINE. @F@@@@          J       XZ
)@@G@@  TRED2             . IF BLANK, O/P IT DIRECT.  @E@@@@          L       YA
)@@G@@  A0,LMAR           . GET LEFT MARGIN.    @G@@@@          TNZ       CRSTYB
)@@G@@P             . DOES CURRENT LINE STOP CAT.     @F@@@@          S       YC
)@@G@@  A0,CCHAR          . NO, SET LMAR AS START.    @^@@@@COPT1     . REENTRYD
)@@G@@Y.    @G@@@@          L         A0,LCHAR          . GET LAST NON-B CHAR YE
)@@G@@IN IMTMP.   @F@@@@          AN        A0,BCHAR          . LESS CURRENT IYF
)@@G@@MTMP POS.   @F@@@@          A         A0,CCHAR          . ADD CURRENT CHYG
)@@G@@AR POSITION.@B@@@@          A,U       A0,1              . +1@E@@@@      YH
)@@G@@    AN        A0,RMAR           . - RIGHT MARGIN.     @F@@@@          TNYI
)@@G@@        A0                . IF NEG THEN IMTMP WILL FIT@D@@@@            YJ
)@@G@@                          . IN IMAGE.     @E@@@@          J         TOOLYK
)@@G@@ONG           . IT IS TOO LONG.     @D@@@@          L         A0,LCHAR  YL
)@@G@@        . GET LAST CHAR.@B@@@@          A,U       A0,1              . +1YM
)@@G@@@F@@@@          AN        A0,BCHAR          . LESS CURRENT POSITION.    YN
)@@G@@@F@@@@          S         A0,NCHAR          . SET FOR COPY OF NCHARS.   YO
)@@G@@@D@@@@          LMJ       X11,TRAP          . DO THE COPY.  @D@@@@      YP
)@@G@@    L         A0,CCHAR          . INCREMENT     @E@@@@          A,U     YQ
)@@G@@  A0,1              . CCHAR TO PROVIDE    @C@@@@          S         A0,CYR
)@@G@@CHAR          . A BLANK.@F@@@@          SZ        PBIL              . CLYS
)@@G@@EAR IMTMP IMAGE LENGTH. @F@@@@          TZ        TXTMOFF           . IFYT
)@@G@@ TX TO BE TURNED OFF,   @D@@@@          J         COPTE11           . DOYU
)@@G@@ NOT READ.  @B@@@@          SNPOFF    . TURN OFF SNOOPY.    @G@@@@      YV
)@@G@@    LMJ       X10,READI         . GET ANOTHER IMAGE IN IMTMP.     @D@@@@YW
)@@G@@          J         COPTE1            . EOF EXIT.     @A@@@@          SNYX
)@@G@@PON     . TURN BACK ON. @D@@@@          L         A0,ASCBL          . GEYY
)@@G@@T BLANK.    @D@@@@          L         A1,IL             . GET LENGTH.   YZ
)@@G@@@C@@@@          S         A0,IMTMP,A1       . SET.    @D@@@@          LMZA
)@@G@@J       X10,TRPAR         . SET IT UP.    @G@@@@          TNZ       CRSTZB
)@@G@@P             . DOES IMAGE CAUSE CONCAT STOP.   @D@@@@          J       ZC
)@@G@@  COPT1             . NO, CONTINUE. @D@@@@          J         COPTE     ZD
)@@G@@        . YES, EXIT.    @]@@@@TOOLONG   . @F@@@@          LMJ       X11,ZE
)@@G@@BOUND         . CHECK ON WORDS TO COPY.   @B@@@@          SNPTX     . SNZF
)@@G@@AP CONTROL WORDS. @E@@@@          TNZ       A4                . CAN ANY ZG
)@@G@@BE COPIED?  @C@@@@          J         COPT3             . NO.     @]@@@@ZH
)@@G@@COPT2     . @F@@@@          LMJ       X11,TRAP          . COPY OVER STRIZI
)@@G@@NG OF WORDS.@D@@@@          J         COPTE             . RETURN IMAGE. ZJ
)@@G@@@C@@@@COPT3     . CHECK IF WE MUST O/P LONG WORD.     @G@@@@          L ZK
)@@G@@        A0,CCHAR          . GET CURRENT IMAGE POSITION.     @F@@@@      ZL
)@@G@@    TE,U      A0,1              . AT BEGINNING OF IMAGE.    @D@@@@      ZM
)@@G@@    J         COPTE             . NO, EXIT.     @D@@@@          LMJ     ZN
)@@G@@  X11,TRAP          . COPY OVER.    @E@@@@          TNZ       CRREM     ZO
)@@G@@        . TEST IF AT END.     @D@@@@          SZ        PBIL            ZP
)@@G@@  . YES, CLEAR.   @C@@@@          J         COPTE             . EXIT.   ZQ
)@@G@@@^@@@@COPTE1    . EOF EXIT.   @A@@@@          SNPON     . SNOOPY ON.    ZR
)@@G@@@C@@@@          SZ        DC1               . CLEAR.  @D@@@@          SZZS
)@@G@@,S1     ICW               . CLEAR S1, TOO.@E@@@@          S         RC,AZT
)@@G@@C             . SET TO REQUESTED CY.@D@@@@          SZ        DC        ZU
)@@G@@        . CLEAR DC FLAG.@F@@@@          SNA       RC,AC1            . SEZV
)@@G@@T INSERTED THIS PASS.   @D@@@@          SZ        OK                . SEZW
)@@G@@T FLAG.     @B@@@@COPTE11   . ENTRY IF TX TO BE STOPPED.    @F@@@@      ZX
)@@G@@    SZ        TXTMOFF           . CLEAR TO BE STOPPED FLAG. @E@@@@      ZY
)@@G@@    SZ        TXTM              . CLEAR TEXT MODE.    @D@@@@          L,ZZ
)@@G@@U       A0,IMAGE          . RESET BUFFER. @C@@@@          S,H2      A0,EAA
)@@G@@DIN+8         . SET.    @G@@@@          SZ        PBIL              . TOAB
)@@G@@ FORCE READ AT NEXT ENTRY.    @#@@@@COPTE     . EXIT  @F@@@@          TZAC
)@@G@@        TXTMOFF           . TEST IF TO BE TURNED OFF. @D@@@@          TZAD
)@@G@@        PBIL              . AND PBIL IS 0.@D@@@@          J         $+2 AE
)@@G@@              . NO, NORMAL.   @D@@@@          J         COPTE11         AF
)@@G@@  . YES, TURN OFF.@G@@@@          LMJ       X11,BBLNK         . BLANK ENAG
)@@G@@D, AND SET LENGTH IN IL.@F@@@@          L         A0,BCHAR          . GEAH
)@@G@@T CURRENT IMTMP POINTER.@F@@@@          TZ        PBIL              . TEAI
)@@G@@ST IF IMTMP EMPTY, OR   @E@@@@          TNE       A0,LMAR           . ORAJ
)@@G@@ AT BEGINNING.    @F@@@@          J         COPTE2            . IF SO DOAK
)@@G@@ NOT ADJUST BCHAR.@D@@@@          TE,U      A0,1              . IF =1, SAL
)@@G@@KIP.  @F@@@@          LMJ       X11,BMOVE         . MOVE BCHAR TO NON BLAM
)@@G@@ANK.  @]@@@@COPTE2    . @D@@@@          L         X10,TRX10S        . REAN
)@@G@@LOAD LINK.  @D@@@@          L         X9,R4             . RELOAD X9.    AO
)@@G@@@ @@@@          SNPOFF    . OFF.    @B@@@@          SNPTX     . SNAP CONAP
)@@G@@TROL WORDS. @D@@@@          J         1,X10             . NORMAL RETURN.AQ
)@@G@@@]@@@@/         . @F@@@@          . THIS ROUTINE IS THE SDF WRITE ROUTINAR
)@@G@@E: LMJ X10,WRB .  @]@@@@          . @]@@@@WRB*      . @E@@@@          TZAS
)@@G@@        ROPT              . IS IT READ ONLY.    @E@@@@          J       AT
)@@G@@  WRB1              . YES, SKIP WRITE.    @E@@@@          L         A0,IAU
)@@G@@CW            . GET IM CNTRL WORD.  @D@@@@          JZ        A0,0,X10  AV
)@@G@@        . RET IF ZERO.  @ @@@@          LA        A0,IL     @D@@@@      AW
)@@G@@    TNE,U     A0,077            . EOF IMAGE ?   @D@@@@          J       AX
)@@G@@  0,X10             . YES, RETURN   @G@@@@          LA        A1,ICW    AY
)@@G@@        . TRANSFER IMAGE CONTROL WORD     @B@@@@          SA        A1,OAZ
)@@G@@CW            .   @E@@@@          TNZ       PRFIL             . IS IT PRBA
)@@G@@INTFILE?    @B@@@@          J         OCWT              . NO@D@@@@      BB
)@@G@@    TP        ICW               . CONTROL IMAGE?@C@@@@          J       BC
)@@G@@  OCWT              . YES     @E@@@@          TZ        DC1             BD
)@@G@@  . WAS IT DELETED?     @E@@@@          J         WRB1              . DOBE
)@@G@@ NOT FILE IT.     @C@@@@          SZ,H2     OCW               . OCW.    BF
)@@G@@@D@@@@          L,S4      A1,ICWS           . GET SPACING   @C@@@@      BG
)@@G@@    S,S4      A1,OCW            . SET IT  @E@@@@          L,S3      A1,IBH
)@@G@@CWS           . GET FULL PRINTFILE  @C@@@@          S,S3      A1,OCW    BI
)@@G@@        . SPACING.@]@@@@OCWT      . @B@@@@          LA,U      A0,EDOUT  BJ
)@@G@@        .   @D@@@@          LMJ       X11,SDFO          . WRITE IMAGE   BK
)@@G@@@ @@@@          J         IOERR     @]@@@@WRB1      . @E@@@@          SZBL
)@@G@@        ICW               . CLEAR REQUIRED HERE.@ @@@@          J       BM
)@@G@@  0,X10     @D@@@@PACK*     . ROUTINE TO PACK LINE FROM IMAG80 TO IMAGE.BN
)@@G@@@B@@@@          LA        A1,LENGTH         .   @F@@@@          JZ      BO
)@@G@@  A1,0,X10          . RETURN ON ZERO LENGTH     @B@@@@          A,U     BP
)@@G@@  A1,3              . +3@D@@@@          SSL       A1,2              . DIBQ
)@@G@@V BY 4.     @E@@@@          S         A1,IL             . SET NEW LENGTHBR
)@@G@@.     @D@@@@          LA        A0,(1,0)          . PACK IMAG80   @B@@@@BS
)@@G@@          LA        A1,(1,1)          .   @B@@@@          LA        A2,(BT
)@@G@@1,IMAGE)      .   @]@@@@PAC1      . @B@@@@          L         A3,IMAG81,BU
)@@G@@A1      .   @B@@@@          EX        STORE,*A0         .   @B@@@@      BV
)@@G@@    TLEM      A1,LENGTH         .   @B@@@@          J         PAC1      BW
)@@G@@        .   @E@@@@          TNE       A0,(1,0)          . AT WORD BOUNDABX
)@@G@@RY ?  @ @@@@          J         0,X10     @E@@@@          L         A3,ABY
)@@G@@SCBL          . NO, PAD WITH BLANKS.@C@@@@          EX        STORE,*A0 BZ
)@@G@@        . TO END  @C@@@@          TE        A0,(1,0)          . OF WORD.CA
)@@G@@@B@@@@          J         $-2               .   @C@@@@          J       CB
)@@G@@  0,X10             . RETURN. @]@@@@STORE*    . @B@@@@          SA,Q1   CC
)@@G@@  A3,0,A2           .   @B@@@@          SA,Q2     A3,0,A2           .   CD
)@@G@@@B@@@@          SA,Q3     A3,0,A2           .   @ @@@@          LMJ     CE
)@@G@@  X9,$+1    @ @@@@          SA,Q4     A3,0,*A2  @ @@@@          LA      CF
)@@G@@  A0,(1,0)  @^@@@@          J         0,X9@ @@@@LOAD*     . LOAD EX TABLCG
)@@G@@E.    @B@@@@          L,Q1      A3,0,X10          .   @B@@@@          L,CH
)@@G@@Q2      A3,0,X10          .   @B@@@@          L,Q3      A3,0,X10        CI
)@@G@@  .   @D@@@@          LMJ       X9,$+1            . HANDLE END.   @B@@@@CJ
)@@G@@          L,Q4      A3,0,*X10         .   @C@@@@          L         A1,(CK
)@@G@@1,0)          . RESET.  @C@@@@          J         0,X9              . RECL
)@@G@@TURN. @^@@@@          . DATA AREA.  @B@@@@          FIELDATA  . SET TO FCM
)@@G@@IELDATA.    @E@@@@FORLB     'FOR-V '                    . FORTRAN I/O LACN
)@@G@@BEL.  @G@@@@FORDA     ' D/A (R-OPT)'              . INDICATES DIRECT ACCCO
)@@G@@ESS FV.     @E@@@@FTNT1     'FTN UNIT #:'               . FTN FORMATTED CP
)@@G@@FILE. @E@@@@FTNT2     '   DATE:    '              . FOR DATE IN LABEL.  CQ
)@@G@@@^@@@@          END       .   ___       L,S4      A1,ICWS           . GECR
)@@G@@*[@@@@*SDFF*@F@@_@       THE FACT THAT THIS PROCESSOR IS, UNDER SYSTEMS CS
)@@G@@LEVEL 30 OR @F@@@@ABOVE, APPROPRIATELY A DYNAMIC (OR POSSIBLY STATIC) COCT
)@@G@@MMON BANK,  @F@@@@AND, UNDER EARLIER SYSTEMS, A REP, MAKES ITS INSTALLATCU
)@@G@@ION A BIT   @G@@_@COMPLICATED. THE STANDARD RELEASED SYSTEM IS CONFIGURECV
)@@G@@D AS A MULTI-BANK @B@@_@PROGRAM, AND FOR USE AS A COMMON BANK.    @A@@_@CW
)@@G@@FOR PRE LEVEL 30 SITES NOTE THAT THE@F@@_@ABSOLUTES: EDQT, EDQC$, AND EDCX
)@@G@@QX HAVE BEEN CREATED USING THE NEW  @G@@_@COLLECTOR. THEY WILL NOT EXECUCY
)@@G@@TE ON EARLIER SYSTEMS. ALSO, ALL MAPS     @F@@@@WHICH HAVE 'P1' IN THEIRCZ
)@@G@@ NAMES ARE FOR CREATION OF THE P1 VERSION.@F@@@@THE RUNSTREAM 'MQNLIST' DA
)@@G@@IS INCLUDED TO INDICATE A USEFUL WAY OF   @G@@_@MAKING A LISTING OF THE DB
)@@G@@EDITOR SYMBOLICS. IT ALSO INCLUDES CALLS ON     @E@@_@THE COLLECTOR TO PDC
)@@G@@RODUCE THE VARIOUS POSSIBLE ABSOLUTES.    @[@@@@      @E@@@@       FOR UDD
)@@G@@SE AS A COMMON BANK, EDQ MUST BE GIVEN A BDI, A @E@@@@'BANK' STATEMENT MDE
)@@G@@UST BE INCLUDED IN THE SYSGEN, AND THE BDI@O@@_@MUST BE IN THE ELEMENT 'DF
)@@G@@CERU$' IN RLIB$, OR IN A FILE REFERENCED IN THE MAP OF THE EXEC. THE BDIDG
)@@G@@ WHICH IS CURRENTLY     @#@@_@USED FOR EDQC$ IS:@[@@_@      @^@@_@EDQC$*DH
)@@G@@  EQU   0400015  .@[@@_@      @A@@_@THE REENTRANT BANK STATEMENT IS:    DI
)@@G@@@[@@_@      @B@@_@REENTRANT BANKS,D+W ARE  'EDQC$',EDQC$    @[@@_@      DJ
)@@G@@@[@@@@      @A@@@@       HERE ARE SOME GENERAL HINTS: @[@@@@      @F@@_@DK
)@@G@@1. EDQ MAY BE RUN AS A MULTI-BANK PROGRAM FROM ANY FILE. A VERSION@G@@_@DL
)@@G@@WHICH WAS MAPPED IN THIS FORM IS IN THE RELEASE FILE WITH NAME EDQX.    DM
)@@G@@@[@@@@      @F@@_@2. THE TWO ABSOLUTES WHICH MUST BE PUT IN SYS$*LIB$ ARDN
)@@G@@E EDQ AND   @G@@_@EDQC$. EDQ IS THE INITIALIZATION PROCESSOR. EDQC$ IS TDO
)@@G@@HE COMMON BANK    @G@@_@WHICH CARRIES ON THE PROCESSING AND TERMINATION DP
)@@G@@FUNCTIONS. EDQ DOES     @F@@_@AN LIJ TO EDQC$. EDQC$ NEVER RETURNS CONTRDQ
)@@G@@OL TO EDQ. IN FACT, THE @D@@_@EDQ IBANK IS COLLAPSED TO RELEASE SWAPFILEDR
)@@G@@ SPACE.     @[@@@@      @F@@@@3. THE EDITOR ALWAYS OPERATES INTERNALLY UDS
)@@G@@SING ASCII CODE, AND IN @F@@_@QUARTER WORD MODE. IT USES AN LPD, SPD SEQDT
)@@G@@UENCE TO ENSURE THAT    @F@@_@QUARTER WORD MODE IS SET. THIS REQUIRES ATDU
)@@G@@ LEAST LEVEL 31.244 ON  @F@@_@AN 1108/6. IN CASE THIS CODE NEEDS TO BE RDV
)@@G@@EMOVED FOR OPERATION ON @G@@_@AN EARLIER EXEC, THE CODE IS LOCATED AT THDW
)@@G@@E BEGINNING OF THE ELEMENT    @F@@_@.INIT. IF THE CODE IS REMOVED THE F DX
)@@G@@OPTION MUST BE USED IN MAPPING@F@@_@BOTH ABSOLUTES. THE ONLY OTHER MAP ODY
)@@G@@PTION IS THE B OPTION WHICH IS@ @@_@ENCOURAGED, BUT NOT REQUIRED. @[@@@@DZ
)@@G@@      @F@@@@4. FINALLY, THE EDITOR CONTAINS AN I BANK CHECKSUM TEST. THIEA
)@@G@@S TEST@G@@_@PERFORMS A CHECKSUM OF THE COMMON BANK EACH TIME A NEW USER EB
)@@G@@IS LINKED   @F@@@@TO IT. THIS REQUIRES ABOUT ABOUT 4K INSTRUCTIONS OF OVEC
)@@G@@ERHEAD PER  @F@@@@USE. HOWEVER, IT SEEMS WELL WORTH IT BECAUSE IF THE I ED
)@@G@@BANK GETS   @G@@_@CORRUPTED IT CAN LEAD TO DISASTER. SINCE IT IS A COMMOEE
)@@G@@N BANK, THE EDITOR@F@@_@TENDS TO STAY IN CORE WITHOUT BEING RELOADED FROEF
)@@G@@M THE SWAPFILE FOR@F@@@@LONG PERIODS (DURING HEAVY USE THIS HAS BEEN SEVEG
)@@G@@ERAL HOURS) AND IF@F@@@@IT GOES BAD, DUE TO HARDWARE OR SOFTWARE FAILUREEH
)@@G@@, EVERYONE LOSES. @F@@@@       IF YOU WISH TO REMOVE THIS CHECK, YOU MAYEI
)@@G@@ SIMPLY DELETE THE@G@@@@LINES OF CODE NEAR THE BEGINNING OF THE ELEMENT EJ
)@@G@@'MCC'. THE FOLLOWING    @B@@@@EDITOR COMMANDS WILL (CURRENTLY) DO IT:   EK
)@@G@@@#@@@@       F MAINR    @]@@@@       D 1 6@]@@@@       @EOF @[@@@@      EL
)@@G@@@G@@_@       IF YOU ALTER THE COMMON BANK IN ANY WAY YOU WILL FIND THAT EM
)@@G@@THE   @F@@@@CHECKSUM FAILS AND YOU GET A MESSAGE WHICH REPORTS THIS FACTEN
)@@G@@. THE @F@@@@MESSAGE GIVES A 24 DIGIT NUMBER. THE FIRST 12 DIGITS ARE THEEO
)@@G@@ OCTAL@F@@@@VALUE OF THE COMPUTED CHECKSUM, THE LAST 12 DIGITS ARE THE SEP
)@@G@@TORED @E@@@@CHECKSUM. THE STORED CHECKSUM IS IN THE ELEMENT 'EDBM'.     EQ
)@@G@@@G@@@@ITS TAG IS HHCHK*. TO INSERT A NEW CHECKSUM SIMPLY CHANGE THE VALUER
)@@G@@E     @G@@@@AT THE TAG 'HHCHK*' TO THE COMPUTED VALUE WHICH WAS PRINTED ES
)@@G@@OUT AND     @E@@@@REASSEMBLE EDBM AND REMAP THE INITIALIZATION PART (.EDET
)@@G@@Q) OF @F@@@@THE EDITOR. THERE IS NO NEED TO REASSEMBLE THE REP. NOTE THAEU
)@@G@@T THIS@F@@@@CHECKSUM TECHNIQUE, SINCE THE STORED CHECKSUM IS AT THE END EV
)@@G@@OF THE@F@@@@USER D BANK, ALSO CHECKS FOR CORRECT LOADING OF THE USER D BEW
)@@G@@ANK.  @[@@@@      @G@@@@       IF YOU HAVE A FILE CALLED, SAY, BOOTLIB WEX
)@@G@@HICH IS ONE OF THE LIB$ @G@@@@FILES TO BE WRITTEN ON THE BOOT TAPE, HEREEY
)@@G@@ IS A RUNSTREAM WHICH WILL    @F@@@@BUILD A COPY OF THE EDITOR AND PUT IEZ
)@@G@@T IN THE FILE READY TO BE     @^@@@@WRITTEN ON THE BOOTTAPE:@[@@@@      FA
)@@G@@@[@@@@      @]@@@@       @RUN @^@@@@       @ASG,T EDTAP,T,XX@^@@@@      FB
)@@G@@ @CAT,P NLB,F     @^@@@@       @USE EDQ$PF,NLB  @ @@@@       @COPIN EDTAFC
)@@G@@P.,EDQ$PF.  @B@@@@       @MAP,NBF EDQ$PF.EDQT/P1MAP,.EDQT   @B@@@@      FD
)@@G@@ @MAP,NBF EDQ$PF.EDQC$/P1MAP,.EDQC$ @B@@@@       @COPY,A EDQ$PF.EDQT,BOOFE
)@@G@@TLIB.EDQ    @B@@@@       @COPY,A EDQ$PF.EDQC$,BOOTLIB.EDQC$ @]@@@@      FF
)@@G@@ @FIN @[@@@@      @F@@@@       NOTE THAT THE USE OF THE @USE ABOVE AVOIDFG
)@@G@@S THE NEED TO     @E@@@@CHANGE THE CONTENTS OF THE EDQ MAP ELEMENTS. THEFH
)@@G@@SE REFERENCE@]@@@@EDQ$PF.     @[@@@@      @F@@@@       HERE IS A SHORT DFI
)@@G@@ESCRIPTION OF THE INSTALLATION STEPS FOR  @F@@@@INSTALLING EDQ AS A COMMFJ
)@@G@@ON BANK UNDER LEVEL 31. IT IS PLANNED FOR @G@@@@FUTURE LEVELS OF THE EXEFK
)@@G@@C THAT THIS PROCEDURE MAY BE SIMPLIFIED. IN     @E@@@@THE MEANTIME THE FFL
)@@G@@OLLOWING COMPLEX PROCEDURE IS REQUIRED:   @E@@@@1. THE FOLLOWING REENTRAFM
)@@G@@NT BANK CARD IS NEEDED IN THE SGS'S:@[@@_@      @B@@_@  REENTRANT BANKS,FN
)@@G@@D+W  ARE 'EDQC$',EDQC$  @[@@_@      @F@@@@2. THE FOLLOWING ENTRY MUST BEFO
)@@G@@ ADDED TO SYS$*RLIB$.CERU$/XXXX     @A@@@@(WHERE XXXX IS THE CURRENT VERFP
)@@G@@SION):@[@@@@      @ @@_@EDQC$*  EQU    0400015    .   @[@@_@      @G@@@@FQ
)@@G@@YOU MAY LIST, OR USE, MQN.CERU$ AS AN EXAMPLE OF A VERSION OF CERU$     FR
)@@G@@@G@@@@WHICH WORKS IN OUR SYSTEM. NOTE THAT THE EXEC MUST BE MAPPED WITH FS
)@@G@@THE   @C@@@@RLIB$ WHICH HAS THIS VERSION OF CERU$ IN IT.    @F@@@@3. THEFT
)@@G@@ FOLLOWING TWO MAP STATEMENTS CREATE THE INITIALIZATION AND @B@@@@COMMONFU
)@@G@@ BANK PARTS OF EDQ RESPECTIVELY:    @C@@@@  (NOTE THAT MAP 25 OR ABOVE MFV
)@@G@@UST BE USED HERE.)@ @@@@ @MAP,BF  MQN.EDQT/P1MAP,.EDQ @A@@@@ @MAP,BF  MQFW
)@@G@@N.EDQC$/P1MAP,.EDQC$    @E@@@@       BEFORE MAPPING YOU SHOULD MAKE SUREFX
)@@G@@ THAT THE ELEMENTS@G@@@@INIT AND EDDBK HAVE BEEN ASSEMBLED WITH THE CORRFY
)@@G@@ECT PROCING FOR THE     @F@@@@COMMON BANK VERSION. THIS PROCING IS CONTRFZ
)@@G@@OLLED BY A FLAG IN THE  @F@@@@PROC ELEMENT, EDPC. THE FLAG IS 'P1SYS'. PGA
)@@G@@1SYS  EQU  1  MEANS THAT@E@@@@COMMON BANK CODE IS TURNED ON AND REP CODEGB
)@@G@@ IS TURNED OFF.   @F@@@@4. NEXT, COPY THESE TWO ABSOLUTES INTO THE SYS$*GC
)@@G@@LIB$ FILES ON     @F@@@@THE BOOTTAPE. IT WOULD BE REASONALBE TO PUT EDQ GD
)@@G@@IN LIB1, BUT EDQC$@#@@@@SHOULD GO IN LIB2.___SSEMBLE EDBM AND REMAP THE GE
